{"tid":669264,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日紀念日同條女去睇Deadpool","createTime":"2018-05-18T10:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T16:14:57.000Z","uid":3954,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3860d40ea2bff7b0d96d626600adcc853304a2f5","tid":669264,"uid":3954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"琴日紀念日 放工之後就搵條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔到去邊好 又見Deadpool上左 咁就諗住一齊睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我條女好好 雖然佢無睇開英雄片 但上次都有陪我睇復仇者3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗今次Deadpool咁多好評 同條女睇實無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好彩 睇緊其間佢笑到唔停口  見佢咁開心我都開心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一播完彩蛋 佢突然大叫:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「DC好睇過Marvel多多聲啦！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢刻我心情：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大笑住同佢講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 「Deadpool都係Marvel黎嫁柒頭！人唔笑狗都吠啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢即刻紅都面哂跑走左...<br />\n到依家佢都已讀不回我 我應該點做...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518271c14c87abc39d988129c8755c5f47cbbd70","tid":669264,